    public abstract class AbstractSortModeNode
extends LazyParent
implements IToolTip
    Implements a second sorting-order. If sortByValue is true, the imminent child nodes are sorted by their value instead of being sorted alphabetically. In this implementation the TreeClickListener is responsible for changing this.
    Author:
    Dominik Hamann, Patrick Haese
